---
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <p class="hero-label">PORTFOLIO · SERVICE PLANNER</p>
    <h1 class="hero-name">
      서정일<span class="name-en">Jeongil SEO</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">
      사용자 여정에서 문제를 발견하고,<br />
      서비스 흐름으로 바꾸는 기획자
    </p>
    <hr class="hero-divider" />
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-num">37,923건</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">앱 리뷰 분석</span>
        <span class="stat-ctx">Gcar VoC 분석</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-num">4개 포맷</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">영상·출판·교육·SNS</span>
        <span class="stat-ctx">콘텐츠 직접 제작</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-num">80%+</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">제작 시간 단축</span>
        <span class="stat-ctx">AI 자동화 파이프라인</span>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <span class="stat-num">3+</span>
        <span class="stat-desc">Years</span>
        <span class="stat-ctx">기획·운영 경험</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #c8e6ff 0%, #ffffff 62%);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 7rem 0 5rem;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: var(--c-sky);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 7vw, 4.25rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 1.08;
    color: #171717;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.1em;
  }

  .name-en {
    font-size: 0.4em;
    font-weight: 400;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    color: var(--c-body);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.2vw, 1.125rem);
    color: #60646c;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-divider {
    border: none;
    height: 1px;
    background-color: var(--c-sky-line);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 320px;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem 1rem;
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--c-sky-deep);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .stat-desc {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--c-body);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .stat-ctx {
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    color: var(--c-sky);
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero-stats {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
